snippet.title: Master Of Time - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
By doncamilo



Thanks to Retro64 for a lot of support

Thanks to Zel for custom actors(Goron,Zora,Guard & checkspot)
Thanks to Nokaubure for aswering to almost all of my questions during the development 

Go to https://hylianmodding.com/ discord server for more

Thanks to the tools & documentations makers

Tools used: 
- Sketchup
- HxD
- zztexview
- SharpOcarina 
- SceneNavi
- Seq64
- MuseScore2
- FL Studio
- Aegh
- https://deku.link/z64-text-editor/

Patch link :
It's for 1.0 USA roms 
.z64:
https://www.mediafire.com/file/k8tbiu1e6y4mevn/MasterOfTime_z64.bps/file
.n64:
http://www.mediafire.com/file/55r3tu0p1n4gjz8/MasterOfTime.bps/file

You can patch here:
https://www.marcrobledo.com/RomPatcher.js/

Soundtrack :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfBIik-g05PI1qMfQPO8flH7bpMKLOUxQ
